column2: SELECT n.objID, n.distance, n.type, p.ra AS pra, p.dec AS pdec, p.modelmag_r, s.bestobjid FROM Galaxy AS G OUTER APPLY dbo.fGetNearbyObjEq (#, #, #) AS n WHERE G.objID = n.objID LEFT JOIN PhotoObj AS p ON n.objid = p.objid LEFT JOIN SpecObj As s ON n.objid = s.bestobjid INTO MyDB.NearbyObjEq
